DESCRIPTION:\n\n10am-3pm October 17th, 2026\n\n\nAll ages welcome, minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\n\nThis is a day for families and individuals to come explore and enjoy Waycross at the beginning of the fall! We’ll have a pumpkin patch, face painting, chili stations, three-legged races, hayrides, and so much more! Folk of all ages are invited to come and join in on the fun!\n
